18
00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:21.720
A group of local cabbies,

19
00:01:21.720 --> 00:01:25.400
who have been dubbed
“The Un-smart Uncles”,

20
00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:28.920
are now providing a new
niche taxi service

